{%- comment -%}
  Happie AI Chatbot Widget
  Floating chat bubble + panel powered by Claude API via Cloudflare Worker.
  Includes email handoff form (Shopify /contact endpoint) and mailto fallback.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- if section.settings.enabled -%}
<div
  id="happie-chatbot"
  data-worker-url="{{ section.settings.worker_url | default: 'https://happie-chatbot-production.up.railway.app/chat' }}"
  data-support-email="{{ section.settings.support_email }}"
  data-bot-name="{{ section.settings.bot_name | escape }}"
  data-greeting="{{ section.settings.greeting | escape }}"
  data-position="{{ section.settings.position }}"
  data-brand-color="{{ section.settings.brand_color }}"
  data-accent-color="{{ section.settings.accent_color }}"
>
  <!-- Floating Chat Button -->
  <button
    type="button"
    class="happie-chat__bubble"
    aria-label="Open chat with Happie Assistant"
    id="happie-chat-open"
  >
    {%- if section.settings.bubble_icon != blank -%}
      <img src="{{ section.settings.bubble_icon | image_url: width: 120 }}" alt="Chat" width="40" height="40">
    {%- else -%}
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
      </svg>
    {%- endif -%}
    <span class="happie-chat__bubble-pulse" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </button>

  <!-- Chat Panel -->
  <div class="happie-chat__panel" id="happie-chat-panel" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="happie-chat-title" aria-hidden="true">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="happie-chat__header">
      <div class="happie-chat__header-info">
        {%- if section.settings.bot_avatar != blank -%}
          <img src="{{ section.settings.bot_avatar | image_url: width: 80 }}" alt="" class="happie-chat__avatar" width="36" height="36">
        {%- else -%}
          <div class="happie-chat__avatar happie-chat__avatar--default">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-7.07 17.07A10 10 0 1 0 12 2zm0 18a8 8 0 1 1 0-16 8 8 0 0 1 0 16zm-4-8a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0zm6 0a1.5 1.5 0 1 1 3 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0zm-1 4.5c-1.5 0-2.8.85-3.4 2.1.6.25 1.25.4 1.93.4 1.5 0 2.8-.85 3.4-2.1a3.85 3.85 0 0 0-1.93-.4z"/></svg>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
        <div>
          <h3 class="happie-chat__title" id="happie-chat-title">{{ section.settings.bot_name }}</h3>
          <span class="happie-chat__status"><span class="happie-chat__status-dot"></span>Online</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__close" id="happie-chat-close" aria-label="Close chat">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
      </button>
    </header>

    <!-- Messages -->
    <div class="happie-chat__messages" id="happie-chat-messages" role="log" aria-live="polite">
      <!-- Greeting populated by JS -->
    </div>

    <!-- Suggested Replies — Category Menu -->
    <div class="happie-chat__suggestions" id="happie-chat-suggestions">
      <div class="happie-chat__cat-label">Popular topics</div>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="What's in every can of Fungi Fusion?">🍄 What's inside</button>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="Tell me about the three mushrooms">🧪 The science</button>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="Which flavors do you have?">🥤 Flavors</button>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="How does Subscribe & Save work?">💸 Subscribe & Save</button>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="Tell me about shipping">📦 Shipping</button>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="What's your return policy?">↩️ Returns</button>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="I need help checking out">🛒 Help with checkout</button>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="Is there a discount for first-time buyers?">🎁 First-order discount</button>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="Does it have caffeine or alcohol?">⚡ Caffeine & alcohol?</button>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="Is it safe to drink daily?">💊 Safety</button>
      <button type="button" class="happie-chat__suggestion" data-suggest="I need help with my order">👤 Talk to a human</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Input -->
    <form class="happie-chat__input-wrap" id="happie-chat-form">
      <input
        type="text"
        class="happie-chat__input"
        id="happie-chat-input"
        placeholder="Type your question..."
        autocomplete="off"
        maxlength="500"
      >
      <button type="submit" class="happie-chat__send" aria-label="Send">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"/><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"/></svg>
      </button>
    </form>

    <!-- Email Handoff Form (hidden by default) -->
    <div class="happie-chat__handoff" id="happie-chat-handoff" hidden>
      <h4 class="happie-chat__handoff-title">Talk to a human</h4>
      <p>Leave us your details and we'll reply within 24 hours.</p>
      <form method="post" action="/contact#contact_form" id="happie-chat-handoff-form" accept-charset="UTF-8">
        <input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="contact">
        <input type="hidden" name="utf8" value="✓">
        <input type="text" name="contact[name]" placeholder="Your name" required>
        <input type="email" name="contact[email]" placeholder="Your email" required>
        <textarea name="contact[body]" placeholder="How can we help?" rows="3" required></textarea>
        <input type="hidden" name="contact[subject]" value="[Happie Chatbot] New customer message — route to orders@livehappie.com">
        <input type="hidden" name="contact[source]" value="happie-chatbot">
        <input type="hidden" name="contact[recipient]" value="{{ section.settings.support_email }}">
        <div class="happie-chat__handoff-actions">
          <button type="button" class="happie-chat__handoff-back" id="happie-chat-handoff-back">← Back to chat</button>
          <button type="submit" class="happie-chat__handoff-submit">Send message</button>
        </div>
        <p class="happie-chat__handoff-fallback">
          Or email us directly at <a href="mailto:{{ section.settings.support_email }}">{{ section.settings.support_email }}</a>
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="happie-chat__footer">
      <span>Powered by AI · Replies may vary</span>
    </footer>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  #happie-chatbot {
    --hc-brand: {{ section.settings.brand_color }};
    --hc-accent: {{ section.settings.accent_color }};
    --hc-bg: #ffffff;
    --hc-text: #1a1a1a;
    --hc-text-muted: #6b6b6b;
    --hc-border: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    --hc-bubble-bg: #f4f4f5;
    --hc-radius: 18px;
    font-family: 'Poppins', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  }

  /* Floating Bubble */
  .happie-chat__bubble {
    position: fixed;
    {% if section.settings.position == 'left' %}left{% else %}right{% endif %}: 24px;
    bottom: 24px;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--hc-brand);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    z-index: 9998;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  }

  .happie-chat__bubble:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .happie-chat__bubble img {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .happie-chat__bubble-pulse {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--hc-brand);
    opacity: 0.4;
    animation: hc-pulse 2s infinite;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  @keyframes hc-pulse {
    0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.4; }
    100% { transform: scale(1.6); opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Panel */
  .happie-chat__panel {
    position: fixed;
    {% if section.settings.position == 'left' %}left{% else %}right{% endif %}: 24px;
    bottom: 100px;
    width: 380px;
    max-width: calc(100vw - 32px);
    height: 580px;
    max-height: calc(100vh - 140px);
    background: var(--hc-bg);
    border-radius: var(--hc-radius);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 9999;
    transform: translateY(20px) scale(0.95);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, opacity 0.25s ease;
  }

  .happie-chat__panel.is-open {
    display: flex;
    transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* Header */
  .happie-chat__header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--hc-brand) 0%, var(--hc-accent) 100%);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .happie-chat__header-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .happie-chat__avatar {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .happie-chat__avatar--default {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .happie-chat__title {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .happie-chat__status {
    font-size: 11px;
    opacity: 0.9;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
  }

  .happie-chat__status-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    background: #4ade80;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .happie-chat__close {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    border: none;
    color: #fff;
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .happie-chat__close:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28); }

  /* Messages */
  .happie-chat__messages {
    flex: 1;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 18px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    background: #fafafa;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  .happie-chat__msg {
    max-width: 85%;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    word-wrap: break-word;
    animation: hc-msg-in 0.3s ease;
  }

  @keyframes hc-msg-in {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .happie-chat__msg--bot {
    background: var(--hc-bubble-bg);
    color: var(--hc-text);
    align-self: flex-start;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
  }

  .happie-chat__msg--user {
    background: var(--hc-brand);
    color: #fff;
    align-self: flex-end;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
  }

  .happie-chat__msg a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .happie-chat__msg strong { font-weight: 600; }

  .happie-chat__msg ul, .happie-chat__msg ol {
    margin: 6px 0 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  /* Typing indicator */
  .happie-chat__typing {
    align-self: flex-start;
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: var(--hc-bubble-bg);
    border-radius: 16px;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
  }

  .happie-chat__typing span {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    background: var(--hc-text-muted);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: hc-typing 1.2s infinite;
  }

  .happie-chat__typing span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .happie-chat__typing span:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

  @keyframes hc-typing {
    0%, 60%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.5; }
    30% { transform: translateY(-6px); opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* Category label */
  .happie-chat__cat-label {
    width: 100%;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--hc-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    padding: 0 4px;
  }
  /* Suggestions */
  .happie-chat__suggestions {
    padding: 0 18px 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    background: #fafafa;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .happie-chat__suggestion {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--hc-border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--hc-text);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .happie-chat__suggestion:hover {
    background: var(--hc-brand);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--hc-brand);
  }

  .happie-chat__suggestions.is-hidden { display: none; }

  /* Input */
  .happie-chat__input-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hc-border);
    background: #fff;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .happie-chat__input {
    flex: 1;
    border: 1px solid var(--hc-border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: inherit;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .happie-chat__input:focus { border-color: var(--hc-brand); }

  .happie-chat__send {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--hc-brand);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.15s, background 0.2s;
  }

  .happie-chat__send:hover { transform: scale(1.06); }
  .happie-chat__send:disabled { opacity: 0.4; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }

  /* Handoff Form */
  .happie-chat__handoff {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 76px 0 0 0;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 20px 18px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    z-index: 5;
  }

  .happie-chat__handoff h4 {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    color: var(--hc-text);
  }

  .happie-chat__handoff > p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--hc-text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .happie-chat__handoff input,
  .happie-chat__handoff textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--hc-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .happie-chat__handoff input:focus,
  .happie-chat__handoff textarea:focus { border-color: var(--hc-brand); }

  .happie-chat__handoff textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 80px; }

  .happie-chat__handoff-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .happie-chat__handoff-back {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--hc-border);
    color: var(--hc-text-muted);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 13px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .happie-chat__handoff-submit {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--hc-brand);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .happie-chat__handoff-fallback {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--hc-text-muted);
    margin: 14px 0 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .happie-chat__handoff-fallback a { color: var(--hc-brand); }

  /* Footer */
  .happie-chat__footer {
    padding: 8px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--hc-text-muted);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hc-border);
    background: #fafafa;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .happie-chat__panel {
      width: calc(100vw - 16px);
      /* Use dvh so the panel doesn't extend behind the mobile browser address bar */
      height: calc(100vh - 180px);          /* fallback for older browsers */
      height: calc(100dvh - 120px);         /* dvh = the actually visible viewport */
      max-height: calc(100dvh - 120px);
      bottom: 80px;
      {% if section.settings.position == 'left' %}left{% else %}right{% endif %}: 8px;
    }
    .happie-chat__bubble {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      bottom: 16px;
      {% if section.settings.position == 'left' %}left{% else %}right{% endif %}: 16px;
    }
    /* Make the X button bigger and more tappable on mobile */
    .happie-chat__close {
      width: 36px !important;
      height: 36px !important;
      font-size: 18px !important;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  (function() {
    var widget = document.getElementById('happie-chatbot');
    if (!widget) return;

    var workerUrl = widget.dataset.workerUrl || '';
    var supportEmail = widget.dataset.supportEmail || '';
    var botName = widget.dataset.botName || 'Happie Assistant';
    var greeting = widget.dataset.greeting || "Hey! I'm the Happie Assistant. Reach our team at orders@livehappie.com or ask me anything below.";

    // ── LOCAL KNOWLEDGE BASE ──────────────────────────────────────────────
    // Answered instantly without backend calls. Pattern-matched by keyword regex.
    // Backend is still hit for anything that doesn't match.
    var KNOWLEDGE = [
      // ── PRODUCT BASICS ──
      {
        match: /what.*(in|inside|is in|contain).*(can|fungi|happie|drink|product)|ingredients|whats? in/i,
        reply: "**Every can of Happie Fungi Fusion contains 2,000mg total of dual-extracted, fruiting-body mushroom extract:**\n\n- **900mg Lion's Mane** — for focus & mental clarity\n- **700mg Cordyceps** — for natural, caffeine-free energy\n- **400mg Reishi** — for calm & stress support\n\nPlus: Carbonated water, organic light agave nectar, citric acid, natural flavor, ocean-derived magnesium & calcium citrate. **Zero alcohol. Zero caffeine. ~40 calories. Vegan, non-GMO, gluten-free.**\n\nWant to read the full science? Check out our [Science page](/pages/the-science)."
      },
      {
        match: /three mushrooms|3 mushrooms|tell me about (the |)(mushrooms|adaptogens|science)|how (does|do) (it|they|the mushrooms) work|the science/i,
        reply: "Here's how each mushroom works:\n\n- **Lion's Mane (900mg)** — Contains hericenones & erinacines that support Nerve Growth Factor (NGF). Studied for focus, cognition & mental clarity.\n- **Cordyceps (700mg)** — Supports cellular energy via ATP production (your body's natural energy pathway). Real energy, no caffeine spike or crash.\n- **Reishi (400mg)** — \"The queen of mushrooms.\" Triterpenes regulate your stress response — calm without sedation.\n\nWe use only **fruiting body extracts** (the real mushroom) — never mycelium grown on grain. Each batch is **dual-extracted** (hot water + ethanol) for the full spectrum of beta-glucans and triterpenes, then **third-party lab tested**.\n\nDeep dive: [The Science Behind Happie](/pages/the-science)"
      },
      {
        match: /flavors?|how many flavors|what flavors|which flavors|taste like/i,
        reply: "We have **three flavors**, all available as 6-packs ($23.99) or a 12-pack Variety Pack ($38.99):\n\n- 🔵 [**Blue Razzberry**](/products/blue-razzberry-fungi-powered-seltzer) — tart, candy-bright\n- 🥭 [**Mango Mimosa**](/products/mango-mimosa-fungi-powered-seltzer) — tropical, lightly sweet\n- 🍉 [**Watermelon**](/products/watermelon-fungi-powered-seltzer) — clean, juicy, refreshing\n\nOr try all three with the [**Variety Pack**](/products/happie-fungi-fusion-mushroom-drink-variety-pack). None taste earthy or medicinal — that was non-negotiable for us."
      },
      {
        match: /caffeine|alcohol|alcoholic|caffeinated|stimulant/i,
        reply: "**Zero caffeine. Zero alcohol.** Always.\n\nThe energy you feel comes from **Cordyceps** supporting ATP (cellular energy) production — not from stimulants. No crash, no jitters, no dependency.\n\nSafe to drink any time of day, at any age, in any setting. Many customers use it as an **alcohol alternative** for sober-curious evenings or as a **coffee replacement** for clean morning energy."
      },
      {
        match: /calories?|sugar|sweetener|nutrition/i,
        reply: "**~40 calories per can.**\n\nSweetened with a small amount of **organic light agave nectar**. No refined sugar, no artificial sweeteners, no sugar alcohols (which cause digestive issues for many people)."
      },
      {
        match: /vegan|gluten|gluten[- ]?free|non[- ]?gmo|allergen|dairy/i,
        reply: "Yes to all of the above:\n\n- ✅ **100% Vegan** — no animal products\n- ✅ **Gluten-free**\n- ✅ **Non-GMO**\n- ✅ **No artificial flavors, colors, or preservatives**\n- ✅ Cultivated mushrooms (not wild-harvested)"
      },
      {
        match: /psychedelic|psilocybin|magic mushroom|trippy|hallucina/i,
        reply: "**No — absolutely not.** Happie Fungi Fusion contains only **functional / adaptogenic mushrooms** (Lion's Mane, Cordyceps, Reishi). These are completely different from psilocybin mushrooms.\n\n- Legal in all 50 US states ✓\n- Non-psychoactive ✓\n- Backed by decades of peer-reviewed clinical research ✓\n\nYou can drink it any time and stay completely clear-headed."
      },

      // ── SAFETY / HEALTH ──
      {
        match: /safe.*daily|drink (every|each) day|can i (drink|have) (this|happie) (every|each) day/i,
